{"tid":421870,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(美國) Donald Trump反對加泰羅尼亞獨立公投","createTime":"2017-10-02T14:59:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-03T11:24:20.000Z","uid":134071,"like":7,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"bdd7bc7a9b576c9efd2135ee119743154dc0aea9","tid":421870,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T14:59:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/1666579/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F1666579%2F&d=UuZ1iPTJC%2FYJcpizRsrAQACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=a4309f9d\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/1666579/</a><br />\n<br />\n2017年9月27日 時事脈搏<br />\n特朗普反對加泰羅尼亞獨立公投<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普在周二與西班牙首相拉霍伊會面後向記者表示，雙方一致反對加泰羅尼亞預期本周末舉行的獨立公投。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普表示，希望加泰羅尼亞人民可繼續留在西班牙，因為不這樣做是很愚蠢的。<br />\n<br />\n根據民意調查，贊成獨立的加泰羅尼亞選民將超過半數。"},{"pid":"4f8e121da930d65416a628c906c9be7f8eb25ee0","tid":421870,"uid":49250,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T15:04:04.000Z","msg":"垃撚圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ada282fe946e8788b1d2deef92ecef2df2106a41","tid":421870,"uid":2054,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T15:05:22.000Z","msg":"你顧撚掂北韓先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a739cd99fdc58a412111f18eacefed5deae25a1","tid":421870,"uid":86841,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T15:05:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f1afb97d714e9d774876131c3174a32f415aff7e","tid":421870,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T15:09:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3b0b4d53a50278c208de18ee9439213964e73af","tid":421870,"uid":126329,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T15:09:08.000Z","msg":"好撚柒 成班之前奶侵侵鞋底奶到成隻狗咁<img src=\"/a